{"pv35:0.1":"Petavatthu ","pv35:0.2":"Culavagga ","pv35:0.3":"10. Dhatuvivannapetavatthu ","pv35:1.1":"“Antalikkhasmim titthanto, ","pv35:1.2":"Duggandho puti vayasi; ","pv35:1.3":"Mukhanca te kimayo putigandham, ","pv35:1.4":"Khadanti kim kammamakasi pubbe. ","pv35:2.1":"Tato sattham gahetvana, ","pv35:2.2":"okkantanti punappunam; ","pv35:2.3":"Kharena paripphositva, ","pv35:2.4":"okkantanti punappunam. ","pv35:3.1":"Kim nu kayena vacaya, ","pv35:3.2":"manasa dukkatam katam; ","pv35:3.3":"Kissa kammavipakena, ","pv35:3.4":"idam dukkham nigacchasi”ti. ","pv35:4.1":"“Aham rajagahe ramme, ","pv35:4.2":"ramaniye giribbaje; ","pv35:4.3":"Issaro dhanadhannassa, ","pv35:4.4":"supahutassa marisa. ","pv35:5.1":"Tassayam me bhariya ca, ","pv35:5.2":"dhita ca sunisa ca me; ","pv35:5.3":"Ta malam uppalancapi, ","pv35:5.4":"paccagghanca vilepanam; ","pv35:5.5":"Thupam harantiyo varesim, ","pv35:5.6":"tam papam pakatam maya. ","pv35:6.1":"Chalasitisahassani, ","pv35:6.2":"mayam paccattavedana; ","pv35:6.3":"Thupapujam vivannetva, ","pv35:6.4":"paccama niraye bhusam. ","pv35:7.1":"Ye ca kho thupapujaya, ","pv35:7.2":"vattante arahato mahe; ","pv35:7.3":"Adinavam pakasenti, ","pv35:7.4":"vivecayetha ne tato. ","pv35:8.1":"Ima ca passa ayantiyo, ","pv35:8.2":"Maladhari alankata; ","pv35:8.3":"Malavipakamnubhontiyo, ","pv35:8.4":"Samiddha ca ta yasassiniyo. ","pv35:9.1":"Tanca disvana accheram, ","pv35:9.2":"abbhutam lomahamsanam; ","pv35:9.3":"Namo karonti sappanna, ","pv35:9.4":"vandanti tam mahamunim. ","pv35:10.1":"Soham nuna ito gantva, ","pv35:10.2":"yonim laddhana manusim; ","pv35:10.3":"Thupapujam karissami, ","pv35:10.4":"appamatto punappunan”ti. ","pv35:11.1":"Dhatuvivannapetavatthu dasamam. ","pv35:12.1":"Culavaggo tatiyo. ","pv35:13.1":"Tassuddanam ","pv35:14.1":"Abhijjamano kundiyo, ","pv35:14.2":"rathakari bhusena ca; ","pv35:14.3":"Kumaro ganika ceva, ","pv35:14.4":"dve ludda pitthipujana; ","pv35:14.5":"Vaggo tena pavuccatiti. "}